text: Joseph de Sonay (born 6 December 1896, date of death unknown) was a Belgian diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1896 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Belgian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Belgium Category:Divers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
